---
title: Creamy Zucchini Orzotto with Toasted Panko & Lemony Arugula Salad
description: What’s orzotto? Glad you asked! You’ll cook rice-shaped orzo pasta like risotto by adding liquid to a pan and stirring over heat. Stir savory roasted zucchini into that creamy, comforting orzotto, shower with buttery toasted panko breadcrumbs and serve with a crisp arugula and almond salad and squeeze of fresh lemon juice for a bright finish.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f2d9fe1e86f3e65846fa1d-142e81bf.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66f2d9fe1e86f3e65846fa1d-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Southern Europe
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-zucchini-orzotto-66f2d9fe1e86f3e65846fa1d
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 870 kcal
